  "detailed_description": "<i>Cat Express</i> is a relaxing and healing game that combines running, fishing, and collecting.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Express Delivery<br>By jumping and dodging various obstacles, deliver express to the people in the town.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617470/extras/7cd8743da6307079847d0f05c7336c5e.poster.avif?t=1699231476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617470/extras/7cd8743da6307079847d0f05c7336c5e.webm?t=1699231476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617470/extras/7cd8743da6307079847d0f05c7336c5e.mp4?t=1699231476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> Customize Cat Room<br>Use the coins earned through delivering express to buy various furniture to customize the cat room.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617470/extras/26060970801c3ca9e854c37e04883517.poster.avif?t=1699231476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617470/extras/26060970801c3ca9e854c37e04883517.webm?t=1699231476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617470/extras/26060970801c3ca9e854c37e04883517.mp4?t=1699231476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> Fishing<br>Casual fishing, catch all kinds of fish and sell them for a good price at the fish store!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617470/extras/1b4d13375b299fa4a8131435bd3f4637.poster.avif?t=1699231476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617470/extras/1b4d13375b299fa4a8131435bd3f4637.webm?t=1699231476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617470/extras/1b4d13375b299fa4a8131435bd3f4637.mp4?t=1699231476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
